name: .GV File Extension
summary: Learn about .GV files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Document that contains a text description of graphs of nodes and edges; written in the DOT language and can be read by Graphviz compatible software programs.

content: NOTE: The GV extension was introduced to replace the previous .DOT extension, which is used for Microsoft Word templates.
